channel.title: Needing Assistance...Tried a tutorial and it messed everything up!
channel.description:
I tried to follow the tutorial " 'Javac' Error? Read this ". All worked okay before it, except I couldn't compile. Now when I open up Moparscape 3.1 and try to "runserver" this comes up...
'java' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file. Press any key to continue.
When I try to compile my TestScape Source, the same message appears. Then to top it all off...When I try to Run my TestScape Source, the screen quickly appears then disappears.
Could someone, please, PLEASE help me.
:)
